data.description: Situated right off Glisan St and Burnside just a couple blocks away, you will be minutes away from stores, parks, schools, etc in a great dead end neighborhood with NO HOA! Three spacious bedrooms, open kitchen, attached garage, and two fulls baths. More photos are too come!
